                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Bloom opon the Mountain<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 stated -</l>
                    <l>Blameless of a name - </l>
                    <l>Efflorescence of a Sunset - </l>
                    <l>Reproduced - the same - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Seed had I, my Purple<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Sowing</l>
                    <l>Should<add type="alternate" extent="address">endow - &amp;#x2022; reward</add>
 address the Day - </l>
                    <l>Not - a<add type="alternate" extent="Tropic">Manner</add>
 Tropic of a Twilight - </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="Show">shift</add>
Show itself away - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Who for tilling - to the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Mountain </l>
                    <l>Come - and disappear -</l>
                    <l>Whose be<add type="alternate" extent="her">this</add>
 her Renown -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 or fading - </l>
                    <l>Witness is not here - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>While I state - the Solemn<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Petals -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>Far as North - and East - </l>
                    <l>Far as South - and West<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
<add type="alternate" extent="expanding">disclosing</add>
 expanding -</l>
                    <l>Culminate - in Rest - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And the Mountain to<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the Evening </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="Fit">Strain</add>
Fit His Countenance - </l>
                    <l>Indicating by no<add type="alternate" extent="Muscle">feature</add>
 Muscle </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="His">the -</add>
His Experience -</l>
                </lg>

